ZH: 这个班级的学生平均年龄为20岁。
EN: The average age of students in this class is 20 years old.

ZH: 平均每小时工作8小时。
EN: The average work hours per day is 8 hours.

ZH: 他的平均分数是85分。
EN: His average score is 85.

ZH: 昨天的平均气温是25摄氏度。
EN: The average temperature yesterday was 25 degrees Celsius.

ZH: 这个公司的平均年收入为100万美元。
EN: The company's average annual income is 1 million dollars.

ZH: 一杯咖啡的平均价格是5美元。
EN: The average price of a cup of coffee is 5 dollars.

ZH: 平均每年有100个人参加这个活动。
EN: An average of 100 people participate in this event each year.

ZH: 这个城市平均每年降雨量为1000毫米。
EN: This city's average annual rainfall is 1000 millimeters.

ZH: 他平均每周练习5次篮球。
EN: He practices basketball an average of 5 times a week.

ZH: 这所学校的学生平均每天花费3小时在学习上。
EN: Students at this school spend an average of 3 hours studying each day.

ZH: 平均每月有20人来参加我们的聚会。
EN: An average of 20 people come to our party each month.

ZH: 这个工厂平均每天生产1000件产品。
EN: The factory produces an average of 1000 products per day.

ZH: 他们平均每周吃4次外卖。
EN: They order takeout an average of 4 times a week.

ZH: 平均每年有50万游客来这个景点参观。
EN: An average of 500,000 tourists visit this attraction each year.

ZH: 这个车队平均每周赢得一场比赛。
EN: The team wins an average of one game per week.

ZH: 他平均每月薪水是4000美元。
EN: His average monthly salary is 4000 dollars.

ZH: 这个州平均每年下雪30天。
EN: It snows an average of 30 days a year in this state.

ZH: 平均每天有5000人搭乘这条地铁线路。
EN: An average of 5000 people ride this subway line every day.

ZH: 这种水果平均每年采摘两次。
EN: This fruit is harvested an average of two times a year.

ZH: 平均每周有十个人在这个公园举办生日派对。
EN: An average of ten people hold birthday parties in this park every week.
